15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 7401-101 of Title 10, unless
18 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. The foster care maintenance payment for Resource Parents who
20 are traditional foster parents shall be at least:
21 1. Twenty-two Dollars and seventy-two cents ($22.72) per day,
22 or Six Hundred Eighty-one Dollars and sixty cents ($681.60) per
23 month, for a child who is zero (0) years to five (5) years of age;
